OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fwarm evening for much of the country.
OL,7,FDry with clear spells for most
OL,8,Fovernight, however low cloud near
OL,9,Feastern coasts will re-develop and
OL,10,Fextend into many central areas by
OL,11,Fdawn. A warn night in the south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FMorning cloud gradually
OL,14,Fclearing, though lingering near North
OL,15,FSea coasts. Otherwise dry with long
OL,16,Fsunny spells. A low chance of an
OL,17,Fisolated shower or thunderstorm in the
OL,18,Ffar south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
